'''戴夫·布拉特'''（David Alan "Dave" Brat；{{bd|1964年|7月27日|||catIdx=Brat}}）是[[美國|美國]]的一位經濟學家和政治人物。

==生平==
自2015年開始，布拉特是維吉尼亞州第七選舉區選出的美國眾議院議員。他的黨籍是[[共和黨_(美國)|共和黨]]。布拉特在2014年6月10日的共和黨內初選中擊敗了眾議院多數黨領袖[[埃瑞克·康特|埃瑞克·康特]]，爆出了一大冷門<ref name=DallasNews20140610>{{cite news |url=http://www.dallasnews.com/news/politics/national-politics/20140610-house-majority-leader-eric-cantor-loses-gop-primary-to-tea-party-challenger.ece |title=House Majority Leader Eric Cantor loses GOP primary to tea-party challenger |work=Dallas Morning News |agency=Associated Press |date=June 10, 2014 |accessdate=June 11, 2014 |archive-date=2014-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140612135012/http://www.dallasnews.com/news/politics/national-politics/20140610-house-majority-leader-eric-cantor-loses-gop-primary-to-tea-party-challenger.ece |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author=Eric Linton |url=http://www.ibtimes.com/house-majority-leader-eric-cantor-defeated-tea-party-challenger-david-brat-virginia-gop-1597736 |title=House Majority Leader Eric Cantor Defeated By Tea Party Challenger David Brat In Virginia GOP Primary |publisher=International Business Times |date=June 10, 2014 |accessdate=June 11, 2014 |archive-date=2020-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029101117/https://www.ibtimes.com/house-majority-leader-eric-cantor-defeated-tea-party-challenger-david-brat-virginia-gop-1597736 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 选举 ==
===2018美国众议院竞选===
{{see also|United States House of Representatives elections, 2018}}
布拉特在2018年竞逐第三个任期，对抗[[Henrico_County,_Virginia|亨利科]]本地人，前中情局官员{{tsl|en|Abigail Spanberger|阿比盖尔·斯潘伯格}}。 此选举被无党派的''{{tsl|en|The Cook Political Report|库克政治报告}}''评为"安全共和党"，直到2017年10月13日，''库克''将其评级更新为"可能共和党"。2018年2月8日，该评级被改为"倾向共和党"，到2018年7月7日，该选举被评为"不分雌雄"。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.cookpolitical.com/analysis/house/virginia-house/va-07-brat-moves-lean-republican-toss |title=存档副本 |access-date=2018-11-29 |archive-date=2018-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180706204424/https://www.cookpolitical.com/analysis/house/virginia-house/va-07-brat-moves-lean-republican-toss |dead-url=no }}</ref>

在一场2018年10月的辩论中，布拉特试图将斯潘伯格描述成一位[[南希·佩洛西|南希·佩洛西]]的信徒。布拉特三番五次地提到佩洛西，以至于开始引起观众哄笑。根据''华盛顿邮报''，保守估计是他提了佩洛西25次。<ref name=":2">{{Cite web|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/local/virginia-politics/rep-brat-and-democrat-spanberger-tangle-in-first--and-likely-only--debate/2018/10/15/03d6615c-d08f-11e8-8c22-fa2ef74bd6d6_story.html|title=Rep. Brat and Democrat Spanberger tangle in first — and probably only — debate|last=|first=|date=|website=Washington Post|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181016165341/https://www.washingtonpost.com/local/virginia-politics/rep-brat-and-democrat-spanberger-tangle-in-first--and-likely-only--debate/2018/10/15/03d6615c-d08f-11e8-8c22-fa2ef74bd6d6_story.html|archive-date=2018-10-16|dead-url=no|access-date=2018-10-16}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/nancy-pelosi-abigail-spanberger-dave-brat_us_5bc52fa4e4b055bc9478f684|title=GOP Congressman Somehow Manages To Mention Nancy Pelosi 21 Times In A Debate|last=Fuller|first=Matt|date=2018-10-16|work=Huffington Post|access-date=2018-10-16|language=en-US|archive-date=2018-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181016163824/https://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/nancy-pelosi-abigail-spanberger-dave-brat_us_5bc52fa4e4b055bc9478f684|dead-url=no}}</ref>

布拉特最终以48.4%比50.4%的票数输给了斯潘伯格，原因很大程度在于在传统共和党强势地区，[[里奇蒙|里奇蒙]]郊区的[[Henrico_County,_Virginia|亨利科]]和[[切斯特菲尔德县_(維吉尼亞州)|切斯特菲尔德县]]发生的巨大转变。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/elections/results/virginia-house-district-7|title=Virginia’s 7th House District Election Results: Dave Brat vs. Abigail Spanberger|access-date=2018-11-07|language=en|archive-date=2018-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181107060246/https://www.nytimes.com/elections/results/virginia-house-district-7|dead-url=no}}</ref>布拉特赢得了选区中7个县中的5个，但斯潘伯格在[[Henrico_County,_Virginia|亨利科]]和[[切斯特菲尔德县|切斯特菲尔德]]以总计30,827票之差淹没了他——总票差6,784票的五倍。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.nytimes.com/elections/results/virginia-house-district-7 |title=Virginia House results from AP |access-date=2018-11-29 |archive-date=2018-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181107060246/https://www.nytimes.com/elections/results/virginia-house-district-7 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

